{"tid":477792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［上水］你班支那賤畜","createTime":"2017-11-23T11:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T11:20:00.000Z","uid":114271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b654081a5054616b9600cafdb67631dd03674b6","tid":477792,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"講緊係紅圈呢班<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/185336_c09137266e424992d9f3f8c60646855f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F185336_c09137266e424992d9f3f8c60646855f.jpg&h=d86122c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冚世界呢個時間排紅van都預左條龍實好長 去埋第個街口<br />\n我大約6點開始排 排到宜家 終於排到隊頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/185759_7690403d0b2897cba355193bba40ccdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F185759_7690403d0b2897cba355193bba40ccdc.jpg&h=3a9b228d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊個唔係放工放學想快快手返屋企食個飯打個飛機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有班拉喼嘅支那賤畜等唔撚切 就跑撚晒去紅圈到截住d紅van唔俾佢地埋站<br />\nD on9小巴佬又俾佢地上<br />\n已紅走撚左四架 有個大嬸打埋電話去投訴都冇用<br />\n結果宜家成班排尾嘅港豬湧撚埋過去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母啊支那賤畜<br />\n死港豬都係 屌埋你地班撚樣</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7e988fa5a398d0f2014c2767de7cb6f6ab4da4ea","tid":477792,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:07:13.000Z","msg":"對上一架走埋 成班隊頭嘅就只可以on99咁等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d66bd99c7edd57d318df9d494c7e69d80925a8","tid":477792,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"趕住去落馬洲丫<br />\n將就下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔去反支真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b8a7a98733f61c33bf1f1164a267f8cda1e8d","tid":477792,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"支針終於吉到落你到啦？<br />\n繼續忍下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}